{"type": "post", "post": {"team": "partnerships", "channel": "pharmacy_partnerships", "user": "mark_watson", "message": "Team, I'm thrilled to announce that as of May 2023, we have successfully integrated 16 pharmacy chains into MediConn Solutions' prescription delivery network. This development significantly increases our reach and accessibility to clients all over the country.", "create_at": 1693920000000}}
{"type": "post", "post": {"team": "sales", "channel": "sales_updates", "user": "julian_lee", "message": "Great news, Mark! This will definitely provide a boost to our potential customer base and improve our service delivery. Let's make sure the sales team is fully updated on this new development.", "create_at": 1693926000000}}
{"type": "post", "post": {"team": "sales", "channel": "sales_updates", "user": "emily_smith", "message": "Thanks for the update, Julian and Mark. This is a game-changer for us. I'll make sure to incorporate this into our sales strategy and forecast models.", "create_at": 1693932000000}}
